### Test Coach Profile Feature

### 1. Login as Coach (get token first)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "coach@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Get Own Profile (to see current state)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Update Coach Profile with all fields
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "bio": "Experienced coach specializing in productivity and focus management. Helped over 100 clients achieve their goals.",
  "specialization": "Productivity & Focus Management",
  "yearsOfExperience": 5
}

### 4. Update Only Bio
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "bio": "Updated bio text with new information about my coaching approach."
}

### 5. Update Only Specialization
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "specialization": "Life Coaching & Career Development"
}

### 6. Update Only Years of Experience
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "yearsOfExperience": 7
}

### 7. Get All Approved Coaches (public endpoint)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/coaches
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. Get Specific Coach Profile by ID (public endpoint)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/coaches/COACH_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. Test Validation - Bio too long (should fail)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "bio": "This is a very long bio that exceeds the maximum length allowed. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum. Additional text to make it exceed 500 characters limit for sure."
